01:22:46,720 --> 01:22:47,999
Alex! Alex!

1359
01:22:48,000 --> 01:22:49,359
Alex.

1360
01:22:49,360 --> 01:22:52,399
Come on. Hold on. Come on. Hold on.

1361
01:22:52,400 --> 01:22:54,559
