01:23:38,480 --> 01:23:40,479
Listen to you.

1379
01:23:40,480 --> 01:23:42,199
Let him go.

1380
01:23:42,200 --> 01:23:43,559
Now!

1381
01:23:43,560 --> 01:23:45,689
Go ahead.

1382
01:23:46,520 --> 01:23:47,839
Now!

