1387
01:24:06,440 --> 01:24:09,359
You know the one-armed
freestyle, don't you?

1388
01:24:09,360 --> 01:24:10,761
(GRUNTS)

1389
01:24:15,200 --> 01:24:18,559
Hey! Come on, or you'll join them!

1390
01:24:18,560 --> 01:24:20,121
This way.

1391
01:24:36,360 --> 01:24:38,046
(GASPING)

1392
01:24:39,320 --> 01:24:40,926
Hold on, hold on.

1393
01:24:46,840 --> 01:24:48,241
