1474
01:29:31,440 --> 01:29:33,839
<i>Now, that'll bring you
into the bilge pump room.</i>

1475
01:29:33,840 --> 01:29:35,159
Hatch. Hatch.

1476
01:29:35,160 --> 01:29:37,119
<i>Now, it's at the same
level as where you are,</i>

1477
01:29:37,120 --> 01:29:38,639
<i>so there must be some air.</i>

1478
01:29:38,640 --> 01:29:40,041
<i>Have you got it?</i>

1479
01:29:42,080 --> 01:29:43,479
