1527
01:34:43,320 --> 01:34:44,519
We made it.

1528
01:34:44,520 --> 01:34:46,843
Oh, Jack.

1529
01:34:53,440 --> 01:34:55,524
Yes. Yes.

1530
01:34:56,200 --> 01:34:58,762
